EmoVerse-AI: Future Improvement Plans

1)  Optimization of Document Processing Speed: Reduce the current processing time by 15 seconds.

2)  Parent Progress Dashboard: Create a dashboard that allows parents to easily monitor their student's progress.

3)  Image-Based Sentiment Analysis: Introduce the capability to process images and pictures for sentiment analysis.

4)  Voice-Enabled Student-to-Tutor Questions: Allow students to use a microphone for asking questions directly to their tutor.
